cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "a2b — arifOS × AssetOpsBench Bridge"
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata from this file."
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: "Muhammad Arif"
    family-names: "bin Fazil"
    affiliation: "arifOS Federation"
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0000-0000-0000"
repository-code: "https://github.com/ariffazil/a2b"
url: "https://github.com/ariffazil/a2b"
license: "Apache-2.0"
abstract: >
  A thin bridge layer between arifOS's constitutional governance kernel and
  the AssetOpsBench evaluation framework (IJCAI 2026 Industrial Automation
  Challenge). The bridge calls arifOS via JSON-RPC (arif_init → arif_observe
  → arif_judge → arif_seal) and produces VAULT999-sealed evidence for every
  benchmark run.
keywords:
  - arifOS
  - AssetOpsBench
  - industrial AI
  - constitutional governance
  - benchmark
  - IJCAI
  - MCP
  - LLM agent
references:
